{"comments":"Media specifications for Element — images, video, audio, 3D models.\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefines spec types for media elements that render external content:\n- ImageSpec, ImageSource (raster images)\n- VideoSpec, VideoSource, VideoPlayback (moving pictures)\n- AudioSpec, AudioSource, AudioPlayback (sound)\n- Model3DSpec, Model3DSource, Model3DCamera (3D content)\n\nThese specs do NOT reference Element, avoiding module cycles.\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Dimension.ObjectFit (ObjectFit)\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Geometry.Shape (RectangleShape for bounds)\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Temporal.Progress (Progress)\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Color.Opacity (Opacity)\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Specification for image elements.\n\nImages render external raster content (photos, icons, video frames).\nThe bounds define WHERE the image renders, ObjectFit defines HOW.\n\n## ObjectFit Behavior\n\n- `Fill` — Stretch to fill bounds (may distort)\n- `Contain` — Scale to fit within bounds (may letterbox)\n- `Cover` — Scale to cover bounds (may crop)\n- `None` — Natural size, no scaling\n- `ScaleDown` — Like Contain, but never scales up\n\n## Filters\n\nImages can have filters applied (brightness, contrast, blur, etc).\nFilters are applied in order during rendering.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["source",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"ImageSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["bounds",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Shape","Primitives"],"RectangleShape"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["fit",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","ObjectFit"],"ObjectFit"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["opacity",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[141,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[136,1]},"title":"ImageSpec"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[108,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[108,3]},"title":"ImageUrl"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[109,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[109,3]},"title":"ImageDataUri"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[110,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[110,3]},"title":"ImageTextureId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"ImageSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[112,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[112,1]},"title":"eqImageSource"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"ImageSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[117,61],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[114,1]},"title":"showImageSource"}],"comments":"Image source - where the image data comes from.\n\nImages can be loaded from URLs, data URIs, or texture references.\nThe renderer resolves these to actual pixel data.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[110,26],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[107,1]},"title":"ImageSource"},{"children":[],"comments":"Specification for video elements.\n\nVideos render moving picture content (video files, streams, webcam).\nThe bounds define WHERE the video renders, ObjectFit defines HOW.\n\n## Playback State\n\nVideo playback is controlled via the `playback` field. This is pure\ndata describing WHAT the video should be doing — the runtime\ninterprets this to control actual HTML5 video elements.\n\n## Determinism Note\n\nVideo is inherently temporal and external — a video URL may return\ndifferent content at different times. The Element itself is\ndeterministic (same VideoSpec = same rendering instructions), but\nthe actual pixels depend on the video source.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["source",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"VideoSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["bounds",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Shape","Primitives"],"RectangleShape"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["fit",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","ObjectFit"],"ObjectFit"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["playback",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"VideoPlayback"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["opacity",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[200,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[194,1]},"title":"VideoSpec"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[152,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[152,3]},"title":"VideoUrl"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[153,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[153,3]},"title":"VideoBlobId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[154,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[154,3]},"title":"VideoStreamId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"VideoSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[156,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[156,1]},"title":"eqVideoSource"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"VideoSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[161,59],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[158,1]},"title":"showVideoSource"}],"comments":"Video source - where the video data comes from.\n\nVideos can be loaded from URLs, blob references, or stream IDs.\nThe renderer resolves these to playable video data.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[154,25],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[151,1]},"title":"VideoSource"},{"children":[],"comments":"Video playback configuration.\n\nAll fields are bounded Schema atoms:\n- Progress: 0-1 for playback position\n- Opacity: 0-100%, clamped\n- Boolean flags for autoplay/loop/muted\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["currentTime",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["playing",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["loop",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["muted",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["playbackRate",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Media","Video"],"PlaybackRate"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[175,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[169,1]},"title":"VideoPlayback"},{"children":[],"comments":"Specification for audio elements.\n\nAudio elements represent sound sources in the canvas. They can have\nvisual representations (waveform display, spectrum analyzer) or be\ninvisible sound sources with spatial positioning.\n\n## Visual Representation\n\nWhen `visualBounds` is provided, the audio renders a waveform or\nspectrum visualization within those bounds. When `Nothing`, the\naudio is purely auditory with no visual output.\n\n## Spatial Audio\n\nThe `position` field (from visualBounds center) is used for 3D\naudio panning when Web Audio API spatial audio is enabled.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["source",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"AudioSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["visualBounds",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Shape","Primitives"],"RectangleShape"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["playback",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"AudioPlayback"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[266,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[262,1]},"title":"AudioSpec"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[215,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[215,3]},"title":"AudioUrl"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[216,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[216,3]},"title":"AudioBlobId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[217,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[217,3]},"title":"AudioStreamId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["waveform",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Audio","Oscillator"],"OscillatorType"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["frequency",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Audio","Frequency","Types"],"Hertz"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[218,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[218,3]},"title":"AudioOscillator"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"AudioSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[223,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[223,1]},"title":"eqAudioSource"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"AudioSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[229,118],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[225,1]},"title":"showAudioSource"}],"comments":"Audio source - where the audio data comes from.\n\nAudio can be loaded from URLs, blob references, or stream IDs.\nThe renderer resolves these to playable audio data.\n\nAudioOscillator uses bounded Schema types:\n- OscillatorType: Sine, Square, Sawtooth, Triangle (or noise types)\n- Hertz: Bounded frequency value (non-negative)\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[221,8],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[214,1]},"title":"AudioSource"},{"children":[],"comments":"Audio playback configuration.\n\nAll fields are bounded Schema atoms:\n- Progress: 0-1 for playback position\n- Opacity: 0-100% for volume\n- PlaybackRate: 0.25x to 4.0x (bounded)\n- Boolean flags for playing/loop state\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["currentTime",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["playing",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["loop",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["volume",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["playbackRate",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Media","Video"],"PlaybackRate"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[244,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[238,1]},"title":"AudioPlayback"},{"children":[],"comments":"Specification for 3D model elements.\n\n3D models render WebGL content within a 2D canvas region.\nThe bounds define the viewport rectangle where the 3D scene appears.\n\n## Rendering\n\nModels are rendered via WebGL into a texture, then composited\ninto the 2D canvas. This allows 3D content to participate in\n2D layering, transforms, and effects.\n\n## Animation\n\nThe `animationProgress` field controls skeletal/morph animations\nbaked into the model. For models with multiple animations,\nuse `animationName` to select which one plays.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["source",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"Model3DSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["bounds",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Shape","Primitives"],"RectangleShape"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["camera",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"Model3DCamera"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["animationName",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["animationProgress",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["opacity",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[324,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[317,1]},"title":"Model3DSpec"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[277,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[277,3]},"title":"ModelUrl"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[278,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[278,3]},"title":"ModelGeometryId"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"Model3DSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[280,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[280,1]},"title":"eqModel3DSource"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Core","Media"],"Model3DSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[284,63],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[282,1]},"title":"showModel3DSource"}],"comments":"3D model source - where the model data comes from.\n\nModels can be loaded from URLs or pre-loaded geometry references.\nSupported formats: glTF (.gltf, .glb), OBJ, FBX\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[278,27],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[276,1]},"title":"Model3DSource"},{"children":[],"comments":"Camera configuration for 3D model viewport.\n\nDefines how the 3D scene is viewed. Uses orbit-style camera\nwith distance, azimuth (horizontal), and elevation (vertical).\n\nAll fields are bounded Schema atoms:\n- PositiveLength: Strictly positive distance (> 0)\n- Degrees: Angle in degrees (bounded, wrapping for azimuth)\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["distance",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Distance"],"PositiveLength"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["azimuth",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Angle"],"Degrees"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["elevation",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Angle"],"Degrees"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["fov",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Angle"],"Degrees"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[299,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Core/Media.purs","start":[294,1]},"title":"Model3DCamera"}],"name":"Hydrogen.Element.Core.Media","reExports":[]}